quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Have you seen someone who rejects religion
  107,2,That is the person who pushes the orphan aside
  107,3,and does not promote feeding the needy
  107,4,It will be too bad for the prayerful
  107,5,who are absent-minded as they pray
  107,6,who aim to be noticed
  107,7,while they hold back contributions